<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued February 23 at 3:30AM CST until February 23 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Midland-Odessa</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM CST THIS
EVENING...
* WHAT...Freezing rain and drizzle. Additional ice accumulations
of a light glaze.
* WHERE...Borden, Scurry, Mitchell and Howard Counties.
* WHEN...Until 6 PM CST this evening.
* IMPACTS...Very slippery sidewalks, roads and bridges are
possible. The hazardous conditions could impact the morning or
evening commute.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling. Prepare for possible
power outages.
The latest road conditions can be obtained by calling 800-452-
9292.</instruction>
